node.text:
Jason Baker @dreamtraxx and myself are teaming up to bring you @redbull Imagination 2.0! 

The foundation was built and layed last year and the course has sat and baked for a year! For round 2 we want to open up the options for the riders with the goal of creating our version, of a dirt skate park! 

More riders with some new fresh faces, plenty more options, and nothing but fun! 

The only rule, there are no rules.. Whatever you see, goes! 

More info to come soon! Stay tuned! 

See y’all in Kansas! 🍻🙌🏼

@redbullmotorsports @e3ranchks @e3foundation 

#redbullimagination2 #e3ranch #freeride

node.text:
@gopro Cat and mouse with @kendallnorman! Talk about a sandy crack.. 😂😭🐈🐁
Thanks @johnnycampbell11x for loaner bike so I didn’t run out of gas hahaha! 😂🙌🏼

The @trimblecec crew brought some of the best heavy equipment operators together with @dreamtraxx and @motosandbox to bring you Dirtkhana 2! The technology these guys were able to use to build us this playground was super rad to see first hand! It will be cool to see these products make their way into the moto realm! Thanks for having us @trimblecec and crew! 
FT. @ryanvillopoto @toddpotter1 @alexmartin_26 @locurcio47 and myself! 🤘🏼🚜
#dirtkhana2 #trimble

node.text:
Our last day in Queenstown was a rad one! I split off with @carsonstorch @reedboggs and @helibikenz to scout some chute lines for the boys to film with @yo_its_jp and Henry Van Asch, while the rest of the crew @gypsytalespodcast and @jaydenfabry met up with @wynmasters and local shredder @badlam1 to rip up the local grass track! Fun times were had all around before heading off to @farm_jam! Stay tuned as we make our way down to the best event of all time! 🙌🏼🇳🇿
#sheepsaretight

node.text: Down days in Queenstown aren’t so bad! Take a stroll with us on the @goldfieldsjet Jetboat with @southernlakesimages at the wheel, and follow along as the boys tag along with @carsonstorch on the infamous @kellymcgarryfoundation “Dream-Track” line!

node.text: Epic few days in Queenstown, NZ watching the boys shred the infamous Gorge Road trails and enjoying one of the most amazing places in the world! Can’t thank @redbullnz enough for letting us crash at the Red Bull base camp! Insane times, and many more to be had! 🙌🏼🇳🇿

node.text:
Take a ride along with me and stay up to date on my trip. Unfortunately I took the digger, and the most important thing was to take care of my health and get my body back to fighting shape for @farm_jam! In the meantime I got to sneak out to the local secret sand track and watch the aussie moto champ @toddwaters47 do his thing! From there it was back to the ankle work! Can’t thank Dr. Chris Brady enough for looking after me while In Australia. But I’m now in Queenstown, NZ working with @remarkablephysios to make sure the ankle is working properly for the weekend Jam! Keep checking back later this week and see what we’ve been up to while on the road in one of the most beautiful places in the world! 🙌🏼✌🏼
@fasthouse_ @gypsytalespodcast @jaydenfabry

node.text:
Jason Baker @dreamtraxx and myself are teaming up to bring you @redbull Imagination 2.0! 

The foundation was built and layed last year and the course has sat and baked for a year! For round 2 we want to open up the options for the riders with the goal of creating our version, of a dirt skate park! 

More riders with some new fresh faces, plenty more options, and nothing but fun! 

The only rule, there are no rules.. Whatever you see, goes! 

More info to come soon! Stay tuned! 

See y’all in Kansas! 🍻🙌🏼

@redbullmotorsports @e3ranchks @e3foundation 

#redbullimagination2 #e3ranch #freeride

⚡️Attention all 805 Friends & Fam⚡️

Tomorrow, August 7th, We celebrate the life of my Grandpa “Captain” Ron Bereman @capnron653 for his final checkered flag! 

The Ol’ fart didn’t want a funeral, so we’re Gona have one last shindig for to celebrate his life! 

If you are able, or have known The man himself, then feel free to come by and share your best “Captain” stories, have some hot fresh BBQ, and enjoy some ice cold @805beer! 

Rest in power Captain! You will be deeply missed, but legends never die! 

See you on the other side Gramps! ❤️🙏🏻

Location: 
9990 Old Morro Rd. East
Atascadero, CA 93422

Tomorrow, Saturday, August 7th
12-6PM

📸 @shirkyyy 
🎨 🖼 @scottdicksonart 

#godspeed #4captain #rip #celebrationoflife #legendsneverdie

node.text:
My last jump on the QP at @xgames was a bit of a nail biter.. I knew I was last jump, and I knew I had to risk it for the biscuit! Went full hallow head and gave her the onion which stood me up more than I anticipated leaving the ramp.. I knew I was in the clear after leaving the ramp, but at the peak of my air, I realized I was way to close to the concrete blocks for comfort.. For as bad as it went, it couldn’t have gone any better! Thankful to walk away clean! I think it’s safe to say @capnron653 was ridin with me on that last jump! 🙏🏻🙌🏼
⚡️Swipe 👈🏼 for the photo sequence⚡️
🎥 @banks169
📸 @ryneswanberg X @octopi.media
#puckerfactor #quarterpipe #xgames

node.text:
With years of wear and tear on my body, it requires some serious TLC! This @purekana roll on muscle and joint gel is my go to after long days of riding! I’ll be 30 next month, and my body feels 60, but damn, I wouldn’t change it for a thing! @purekanaactionsports 🙌🏼🍻
📸 @maxmandell_ 
#purekana #cbd
